ate#18181, gender#18182]\n   +- LocalRelation [department#18183, manager#18184]\n\n== Physical Plan ==\nAdaptiveSparkPlan isFinalPlan=false\n+- == Initial Plan ==\n   PhotonResultStage\n   +- PhotonColumnarToRow\n      +- PhotonProject [department#18177, emp_id#18174L, name#18175, designation#18176, salary#18178L, city#18179, age#18180L, joining_date#18181, gender#18182, manager#18184]\n         +- PhotonBroadcastHashJoin [department#18177], [department#18183], Inner, BuildRight, false, true\n            :- PhotonRowToColumnar\n            :  +- LocalTableScan [emp_id#18174L, name#18175, designation#18176, department#18177, salary#18178L, city#18179, age#18180L, joining_date#18181, gender#18182]\n            +- PhotonShuffleExchangeSource\n               +- PhotonShuffleMapStage EXECUTOR_BROADCAST, [id=#15411]\n                  +- PhotonShuffleExchangeSink SinglePartition\n                     +- PhotonRowToColumnar\n                        +- LocalTableScan [department#18183, manager#18184]\n\n== Photon Explanation ==\nThe query is fully supported by Photon.\n"
